version 0.1.3
=============

2008-08-23   Fabrice Nicol <fabnicol@users.sourceforge.net>

  * Add long options and code from dvda-author-08.07 (audio2.c, 
    structures.h, audio.h, libc_utils.a) and new command-line interface.
  * Extend command line arguments (several files can be processed).
  * Add --dry and --prune features.
  * Bugfixes.
  * New Windows NSIS installer, rpm and deb packages, upgrade GNU build scripts.
  * Links to static library libfixwav.a 

version 0.1.2
=============

2008-07-3     Fabrice Nicol <fabnicol@users.sourceforge.net>

  * Add features to version 0.1.1:

  - Options -a, -b, -c, -l, -p, -q, -o, -s with getopt syntax.
  - GNU packaging (autoconf tools and docs).
  - Modular structure and Code::Blocks project.
  - Copy mode (-o) to avoid damages to original files.
  - Automatic repair mode.
  - Can prepend new header to raw soundfile.

  * Bugfixes: 

  - Added asserts to secure core processes.

Original code by www.taperssection.com member pigiron downloadable 
from this site (unlicensed code).